title: Ep. 416 - Daya's Plan - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Madhavi tells Bhide about the ghost in the society, but he laughs it off. Daya asks Jethalal to get some items to get rid of the ghost, but she doesn't tell him the real reason.

title: Ep. 417 - Bhide Is Scared - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Madhavi finds Bhide lying in the Balcony, and he narrates the whole ghost story which he had seen last night. Bhide gets so scared that he gets a fever.  Upon knowing this, the whole society gathers at Bhide's house and are shocked.

title: Ep. 418 - Men To Guard The Society - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: All the ladies of the Gokuldham society are scared of the ghost, but the men refuse to believe about it. The men decide to guard society at night and prove that there is no ghost. Daya, according to her mother's advice, plans to send Jethalal away.

title: Ep. 419 - Jethalal Meets A Strange Person - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: A worried Daya, calls up Jethalal to ask whether he has started for home as it has become very dark. On his way back home, Jethalal encounters with a strange man, and he gets scared. Jethalal makes excuses to guard society at night.

title: Ep. 420 - Iyer And Popatlal Encounter With The Ghost - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sodhi, Popatlal, and Iyer guard the society at night, but after some time, Sodhi goes to his home. After hearing the shout of Popatlal, the society members go down to find a scared Popatlal and Iyer.

title: Ep. 421 - Black Magic For The Ghost - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: After seeing the scary story of the ghost, everyone is scared at night to sleep in their houses. Sundar gives Daya the idea of calling a person who does black magic to get rid of the ghost.

title: Ep. 422 - Gokuldham Members See The Ghost - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Two men arrive at Gokuldham society to get rid off the ghost. Suddenly, the ghost appears in front of the society members and scare everybody. The society members run into the clubhouse for protection.

title: Ep. 423 - Another Ghost In Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu Sena, along with Rita reporter, tells the society members about what they have discovered related to the ghost and makes a plan. Bit, the twist in the story comes when the ghost meets another ghost in the society.

title: Ep. 424 - The Ghost Story Is Revealed - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: According to the plan, Daya dresses up as a ghost and tries to scare the lady ghost. The ghost is a lady with her set of friends who try to do something illegal in society.

title: Ep. 425 - Tapu Tells A Story - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu reveals to the society members as to how he found the truth behind the ghost story. He also tells that he took the help of Rita reporter, and together they made a plan.

title: Ep. 426 - Parcel For Taarak - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak receives a parcel in which he gets a pen with I love You written on the box. Jethalal and Anjali are suspicious of Taarak. Meanwhile, Anjali receives a call from a girl asking about Taarak.

title: Ep. 427 - Love Letter For Taarak - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Anjali shares her doubt with her society friends who advise her to clear the matter soon. Daya suggests Popatlal and Rita get married to each other, and they both start fighting.

title: Ep. 428 - Anjali's Sister Koyal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak receives a love message from a unknown number and Anjali gets upset with him. When the situation begins to worsen, Anjali's sister Koyal comes into the picture and tells that the prank was played by her.

title: Ep. 429 - Popatlal Dreams About Koyal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal tries impressing Koyal in all possible ways and keeps dreaming about her. In his excitement, he even calls Bhide in the middle of the night to ask about his personality. Popatlal waits to see Koyal and talk to her the next day.

title: Ep. 430 - Lunch At The Gada House - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya invites Taarak's family for lunch at her place, and in sometime Popatlal lands at Taarak's house. Koyal plays many pranks on Popatlal to which he sweetly reacts.
